parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Anti-Lock Brake System (ABS) Failure at Low Speeds
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system at low speeds can cause the vehicle to take longer to stop, increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: The ABS system engages at low speeds (under 10mph)
causing the vehicle to take longer to stop
vibration in the brake pedal
and increased stopping distance.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rusting of Brake Lines and Components
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rusting of brake lines and components can cause brake fluid leaks, leading to a loss of braking power, and increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Brake pedal goes to the floor
loss of stopping power
rusting of brake lines and components
and brake fluid leaks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The premature wear of brake rotors can cause the brake system to fail, leading to a loss of braking power, and increasing the risk of accidents, injuries, and fatalities.
symptoms: Premature wear of brake rotors
rusting of rotors from the inside out
and inability to turn rotors during brake pad changes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the parking brake system can cause the vehicle to roll or move unexpectedly, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The parking brake pedal goes to the floor
the parking brake fails to hold
the vehicle rolls or moves unexpectedly
the parking brake system does not work even when never used.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the multi-function switch can cause the headlights to malfunction, leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: The headlights frequently go out while driving
immediate loss of illumination when using signal lights
high beam stalk
or tilt wheel features.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various electrical components to malfunction, leading to reduced vehicle functionality and increased risk of accidents.
symptoms: Electrical components malfunction
such as headlights
signal lights
and high beam stalk
leading to reduced visibility and increased risk of accidents.
